      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameter ranges documented; sensitivity study not required at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "All model input parameters (viscosity, density, pump speed, flow rate) are documented with nominal values and ranges. A formal sensitivity or uncertainty propagation study is not required at MRL 2 and was not performed."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
